summary: This is a travel authorization notification for a trip related to the 'E stein Investigation' for witness interviews in the United States. The authorization was approved on February 19, 2020, and the trip is scheduled from February 26 to March 2, 2020.

events.title: Scheduled Witness Interview Trip
